title: - Nordstrøm 2 et politisk våpen
cleaned_sentences: The Trump administration warns Europe that the Russian gas line Nordstrøm 2 is a political weapon that will increase the dependence on Russia.
The same media and authorities who have played the Russia Collusion card against Trump ignore that it is they themselves who play Putin right in their hands.
